import numpy as np

def mean_stddev(numbers):
    mean = np.mean(numbers)
    stddev = np.std(numbers)
    return mean, stddev

if __name__ == '__main__':
    numbers = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
    mean, stddev = mean_stddev(numbers)
    print('Mean:', mean)
    print('Standard deviation:', stddev))
